data.description: The moment you approach this property, your eyes are drawn to the elegant archway that gracefully leads you to the front door, a beautiful introduction to the modern exterior design. As you step inside, you are greeted by a soothing and sophisticated neutral color palette, complemented by timeless features that exude charm and character. The layout of the home is thoughtfully designed, offering two spacious living areas and a formal dining room, perfectly catering to your family's needs and making entertaining a delight. The den, adorned with striking natural wood accents and a unique wet bar just off the patio, embodies the blend of character and modern living that defines this home. The living room, featuring exquisite wooden beams, further accentuates the home's unique character, adding warmth and elegance to the space. A true standout feature of this property is the generously sized owner's suite. With an abundance of space, it offers a tranquil sanctuary to unwind and rejuvenate after a long day. The en-suite bathroom has been updated with tasteful fixtures and finishes, including a stunning tiled shower. Practicality and organization are a priority throughout this home, with each room boasting a spacious walk-in closet and additional storage options discreetly placed throughout the house. Moving outside, the well-conceived outdoor space seamlessly complements the indoor experience. The spacious yard offers endless possibilities, whether it be for activities, a place to install a pool, or simply a serene spot to relax in the fresh air.
